Maxima made her way to the entrance. Leaning against it as it opened, 
watching Tyrael & Hydras. 

She growled. "A deal now & back stab later?" 

Glaring at Tyrael, "You do anything treacherous, Tyrael. I will PERSONALLY 
have your lasercore!" hissing as she bit the words out.
